<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="K" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Kin2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Kin,</orth> adj. (never before a subst.) of the same race, related: <cit><quote>lawful mercy is nothing k. to foul redemption,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 2.4.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 4, 113</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my sword and yours are k.</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>k. to Jove's thunder,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.1.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 1, 10</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>those that are k. to the king,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.2.120" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 2, 120</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.2.120" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 2, 120</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.7.72" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 7, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.1.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 1, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.175" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 175</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.92" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.4.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 4, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.2.6" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 112</bibl>.
